Object.Field: LKM Hive to HBase Incremental Update HBASE-SERDE Direct

COMPONENT NAME: LKM Hive to HBase Incremental Update HBASE-SERDE Direct COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.1.3.0.1 and above DESCRIPTION: This LKM loads data from Hive into HBase and supports inserting new rows as well as updating existing data. This is a direct load LKM and must be used without any IKM.
Please see BigDataConnector Documentation for more details.
Check this option if you wish to create the target table
Set this option to true, if you wish to replace the target table content with the new data.
HBase uses a Write-Ahead-Log to protect against data loss. For better performance, WAL can be disabled. Please note that this setting applies to all Hive commands executed later in this session.
